      "content": "he says he's fine though, just really sleepy. he's insisting it's just the jet lag and the pressure from the flight. if he just sleeps it off for a few hours and drinks some water, do you think he'll be okay by the morning? he really doesn't want to go to the ER if he doesn't have to.",
